H

handleEvent(Event) - Method in class Sim
Handles the event accordingly 1) If customer arrives, assign it to cashier 2) If cashiers are busy, make the customer wait 3) If the waiting customers are = waitLineSizeLimit, the next customer is overflown 4) If the customer has been serviced, makes the cashier available
